{
  "video_id": "_wMTKRixZIE",
  "title": "How to get back to work after a career break | Carol Fishman Cohen",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 14280.0,
      "end_time": 17816.0,
      "text": "People returning to work after a career break:"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17840.0,
      "end_time": 20160.0,
      "text": "I call them relaunchers."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20390.0,
      "end_time": 23896.0,
      "text": "These are people who have taken career breaks for elder care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23920.0,
      "end_time": 25736.0,
      "text": "for childcare reasons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25760.0,
      "end_time": 27456.0,
      "text": "pursuing a personal interest"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27480.0,
      "end_time": 29680.0,
      "text": "or a personal health issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30160.0,
      "end_time": 33536.0,
      "text": "Closely related are career transitioners of all kinds:"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 33560.0,
      "end_time": 35896.0,
      "text": "veterans, military spouses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35920.0,
      "end_time": 38336.0,
      "text": "retirees coming out of retirement"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38360.0,
      "end_time": 40800.0,
      "text": "or repatriating expats."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41760.0,
      "end_time": 44695.0,
      "text": "Returning to work after a career break is hard"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44720.0,
      "end_time": 47736.0,
      "text": "because of a disconnect between the employers"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 47760.0,
      "end_time": 49656.0,
      "text": "and the relaunchers."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 49680.0,
      "end_time": 53656.0,
      "text": "Employers can view hiring people with a gap on their resume"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53680.0,
      "end_time": 55775.0,
      "text": "as a high-risk proposition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 55800.0,
      "end_time": 59656.0,
      "text": "and individuals on career break can have doubts about their abilities"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 59680.0,
      "end_time": 61256.0,
      "text": "to relaunch their careers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 61280.0,
      "end_time": 63600.0,
      "text": "especially if they&#39;ve been out for a long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 64319.0,
      "end_time": 69800.0,
      "text": "This disconnect is a problem that I&#39;m trying to help solve."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 69640.0,
      "end_time": 74160.0,
      "text": "Now, successful relaunchers are everywhere and in every field."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 74680.0,
      "end_time": 76416.0,
      "text": "This is Sami Kafala."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 76440.0,
      "end_time": 79176.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s a nuclear physicist in the UK"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 79200.0,
      "end_time": 83120.0,
      "text": "who took a five-year career break to be home with his five children."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 84160.0,
      "end_time": 88960.0,
      "text": "The Singapore press recently wrote about nurses returning to work"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 88120.0,
      "end_time": 90176.0,
      "text": "after long career breaks."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 90200.0,
      "end_time": 92216.0,
      "text": "And speaking of long career breaks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 92240.0,
      "end_time": 93520.0,
      "text": "this is Mimi Kahn."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 94120.0,
      "end_time": 97296.0,
      "text": "She&#39;s a social worker in Orange County, California,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 97320.0,
      "end_time": 100655.0,
      "text": "who returned to work in a social services organization"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 100680.0,
      "end_time": 103456.0,
      "text": "after a 25-year career break."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 103480.0,
      "end_time": 105840.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the longest career break that I&#39;m aware of."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 106280.0,
      "end_time": 108816.0,
      "text": "Supreme Court Justice Sandra Day O&#39;Connor"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 108840.0,
      "end_time": 111680.0,
      "text": "took a five-year career break early in her career."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 112720.0,
      "end_time": 116920.0,
      "text": "And this is Tracy Shapiro, who took a 13-year career break."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 117400.0,
      "end_time": 121336.0,
      "text": "Tracy answered a call for essays by the Today Show"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 121360.0,
      "end_time": 123776.0,
      "text": "from people who were trying to return to work"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 123800.0,
      "end_time": 125640.0,
      "text": "but having a difficult time of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 126160.0,
      "end_time": 130615.0,
      "text": "Tracy wrote in that she was a mom of five who loved her time at home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 130639.00000000001,
      "end_time": 134176.0,
      "text": "but she had gone through a divorce and needed to return to work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 134200.0,
      "end_time": 137136.0,
      "text": "plus she really wanted to bring work back into her life"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 137160.0,
      "end_time": 138799.0,
      "text": "because she loved working."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 139520.0,
      "end_time": 142960.0,
      "text": "Tracy was doing what so many of us do"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 142120.0,
      "end_time": 145856.0,
      "text": "when we feel like we&#39;ve put in a good day in the job search."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 145880.0,
      "end_time": 148856.0,
      "text": "She was looking for a finance or accounting role,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 148880.0,
      "end_time": 151576.0,
      "text": "and she had just spent the last nine months"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 151600.0,
      "end_time": 154896.0,
      "text": "very diligently researching companies online"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 154920.0,
      "end_time": 157679.0,
      "text": "and applying for jobs with no results."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 158120.0,
      "end_time": 161856.0,
      "text": "I met Tracy in June of 2011,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 161880.0,
      "end_time": 165416.0,
      "text": "when the Today Show asked me if I could work with her"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 165440.0,
      "end_time": 167600.0,
      "text": "to see if I could help her turn things around."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 168160.0,
      "end_time": 171616.0,
      "text": "The first thing I told Tracy was she had to get out of the house."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 171640.0,
      "end_time": 174375.0,
      "text": "I told her she had to go public with her job search"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 174400.0,
      "end_time": 178240.0,
      "text": "and tell everyone she knew about her interest in returning to work."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 178680.0,
      "end_time": 182456.0,
      "text": "I also told her, \"You are going to have a lot of conversations"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 182480.0,
      "end_time": 184550.0,
      "text": "that don&#39;t go anywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 184800.0,
      "end_time": 187336.0,
      "text": "Expect that, and don&#39;t be discouraged by it."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 187360.0,
      "end_time": 188936.0,
      "text": "There will be a handful"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 188960.0,
      "end_time": 191800.0,
      "text": "that ultimately lead to a job opportunity.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 192680.0,
      "end_time": 195296.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll tell you what happened with Tracy in a little bit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 195320.0,
      "end_time": 197749.0,
      "text": "but I want to share with you a discovery that I made"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 197773.0,
      "end_time": 199496.0,
      "text": "when I was returning to work"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 199520.0,
      "end_time": 203616.0,
      "text": "after my own career break of 11 years out of the full-time workforce."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 203640.0,
      "end_time": 208880.0,
      "text": "And that is, that people&#39;s view of you is frozen in time."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 209320.0,
      "end_time": 212976.0,
      "text": "What I mean by this is, when you start to get in touch with people"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 213000.0,
      "end_time": 215736.0,
      "text": "and you get back in touch with those people from the past,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 215760.0,
      "end_time": 219160.0,
      "text": "the people with whom you worked or went to school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 219400.0,
      "end_time": 221775.0,
      "text": "they are going to remember you as you were"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 221800.0,
      "end_time": 223616.0,
      "text": "before your career break."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 223640.0,
      "end_time": 227136.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s even if your sense of self has diminished over time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 227160.0,
      "end_time": 229256.0,
      "text": "as happens with so many of us"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 229280.0,
      "end_time": 233176.0,
      "text": "the farther removed we are from our professional identities."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 233200.0,
      "end_time": 235896.0,
      "text": "So for example, you might think of yourself"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 235920.0,
      "end_time": 237399.0,
      "text": "as someone who looks like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 237800.0,
      "end_time": 242960.0,
      "text": "This is me, crazy after a day of driving around in my minivan."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 242120.0,
      "end_time": 244320.0,
      "text": "Or here I am in the kitchen."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 244760.0,
      "end_time": 247296.0,
      "text": "But those people from the past,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 247320.0,
      "end_time": 249536.0,
      "text": "they don&#39;t know about any of this."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 249560.0,
      "end_time": 252960.0,
      "text": "They only remember you as you were,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 252120.0,
      "end_time": 256296.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s a great confidence boost to be back in touch with these people"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 256320.0,
      "end_time": 259959.0,
      "text": "and hear their enthusiasm about your interest in returning to work."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 261440.0,
      "end_time": 265536.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s one more thing I remember vividly from my own career break."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 265560.0,
      "end_time": 268935.0,
      "text": "And that was that I hardly kept up with the business news."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 268959.0,
      "end_time": 270576.0,
      "text": "My background is in finance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 270600.0,
      "end_time": 273160.0,
      "text": "and I hardly kept up with any news"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 273400.0,
      "end_time": 275976.0,
      "text": "when I was home caring for my four young children."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 276000.0,
      "end_time": 279376.0,
      "text": "So I was afraid I&#39;d go into an interview"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 279400.0,
      "end_time": 282760.0,
      "text": "and start talking about a company that didn&#39;t exist anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 283200.0,
      "end_time": 286736.0,
      "text": "So I had to resubscribe to the Wall Street Journal"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 286760.0,
      "end_time": 290216.0,
      "text": "and read it for a good six months cover to cover before I felt"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 290240.0,
      "end_time": 294160.0,
      "text": "like I had a handle on what was going on in the business world again."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 295880.0,
      "end_time": 299536.0,
      "text": "I believe relaunchers are a gem of the workforce,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 299560.0,
      "end_time": 301296.0,
      "text": "and here&#39;s why."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 301320.0,
      "end_time": 303135.0,
      "text": "Think about our life stage:"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 303160.0,
      "end_time": 306816.0,
      "text": "for those of us who took career breaks for childcare reasons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 306840.0,
      "end_time": 308816.0,
      "text": "we have fewer or no maternity leaves."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 308840.0,
      "end_time": 310335.0,
      "text": "We did that already."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 310360.0,
      "end_time": 313696.0,
      "text": "We have fewer spousal or partner job relocations."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 313720.0,
      "end_time": 316176.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re in a more settled time of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 316200.0,
      "end_time": 318150.0,
      "text": "We have great work experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 318400.0,
      "end_time": 320560.0,
      "text": "We have a more mature perspective."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 320800.0,
      "end_time": 323656.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re not trying to find ourselves at an employer&#39;s expense."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 323680.0,
      "end_time": 327896.0,
      "text": "Plus we have an energy, an enthusiasm about returning to work"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 327920.0,
      "end_time": 330840.0,
      "text": "precisely because we&#39;ve been away from it for a while."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 331600.0,
      "end_time": 334216.0,
      "text": "On the flip side, I speak with employers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 334240.0,
      "end_time": 336776.0,
      "text": "and here are two concerns that employers have"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 336800.0,
      "end_time": 338696.0,
      "text": "about hiring relaunchers."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 338720.0,
      "end_time": 341776.0,
      "text": "The first one is, employers are worried that relaunchers"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 341800.0,
      "end_time": 343840.0,
      "text": "are technologically obsolete."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 344400.0,
      "end_time": 345655.0,
      "text": "Now, I can tell you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 345680.0,
      "end_time": 349256.0,
      "text": "having been technologically obsolete myself at one point,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 349280.0,
      "end_time": 350960.0,
      "text": "that it&#39;s a temporary condition."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 351520.0,
      "end_time": 357656.0,
      "text": "I had done my financial analysis so long ago that I used Lotus 1-2-3."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 357680.0,
      "end_time": 360616.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know if anyone can even remember back that far,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 360640.0,
      "end_time": 362856.0,
      "text": "but I had to relearn it on Excel."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 362880.0,
      "end_time": 365960.0,
      "text": "It actually wasn&#39;t that hard. A lot of the commands are the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 366600.0,
      "end_time": 368816.0,
      "text": "I found PowerPoint much more challenging,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 368840.0,
      "end_time": 371000.0,
      "text": "but now I use PowerPoint all the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 371960.0,
      "end_time": 376616.0,
      "text": "I tell relaunchers that employers expect them to come to the table"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 376640.0,
      "end_time": 380135.0,
      "text": "with a working knowledge of basic office management software."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 380160.0,
      "end_time": 381896.0,
      "text": "And if they&#39;re not up to speed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 381920.0,
      "end_time": 384296.0,
      "text": "then it&#39;s their responsibility to get there."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 384320.0,
      "end_time": 385520.0,
      "text": "And they do."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 385960.0,
      "end_time": 389575.0,
      "text": "The second area of concern that employers have about relaunchers"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 389600.0,
      "end_time": 392800.0,
      "text": "is they&#39;re worried that relaunchers don&#39;t know what they want to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 393440.0,
      "end_time": 396656.0,
      "text": "I tell relaunchers that they need to do the hard work"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 396680.0,
      "end_time": 400176.0,
      "text": "to figure out whether their interests and skills have changed"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 400200.0,
      "end_time": 401776.0,
      "text": "or have not changed"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 401800.0,
      "end_time": 403616.0,
      "text": "while they have been on career break."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 403640.0,
      "end_time": 405895.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s not the employer&#39;s job."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 405920.0,
      "end_time": 410496.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the relauncher&#39;s responsibility to demonstrate to the employer"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 410520.0,
      "end_time": 412440.0,
      "text": "where they can add the most value."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 414560.0,
      "end_time": 417840.0,
      "text": "Back in 2010 I started noticing something."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 418400.0,
      "end_time": 422536.0,
      "text": "I had been tracking return to work programs since 2008,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 422560.0,
      "end_time": 425856.0,
      "text": "and in 2010, I started noticing"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 425880.0,
      "end_time": 429776.0,
      "text": "the use of a short-term paid work opportunity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 429800.0,
      "end_time": 432256.0,
      "text": "whether it was called an internship or not,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 432280.0,
      "end_time": 434616.0,
      "text": "but an internship-like experience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 434640.0,
      "end_time": 437776.0,
      "text": "as a way for professionals to return to work."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 437800.0,
      "end_time": 440576.0,
      "text": "I saw Goldman Sachs and Sara Lee"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 440600.0,
      "end_time": 443896.0,
      "text": "start corporate reentry internship programs."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 443920.0,
      "end_time": 448360.0,
      "text": "I saw a returning engineer, a nontraditional reentry candidate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 449120.0,
      "end_time": 452936.0,
      "text": "apply for an entry-level internship program in the military,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 452960.0,
      "end_time": 455320.0,
      "text": "and then get a permanent job afterward."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 455880.0,
      "end_time": 459576.0,
      "text": "I saw two universities integrate internships"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 459600.0,
      "end_time": 462640.0,
      "text": "into mid-career executive education programs."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 463200.0,
      "end_time": 466150.0,
      "text": "So I wrote a report about what I was seeing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 466400.0,
      "end_time": 469160.0,
      "text": "and it became this article for Harvard Business Review"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 469400.0,
      "end_time": 470936.0,
      "text": "called \"The 40-Year-Old Intern.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 470960.0,
      "end_time": 473575.0,
      "text": "I have to thank the editors there for that title,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 473600.0,
      "end_time": 474976.0,
      "text": "and also for this artwork"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 475000.0,
      "end_time": 479336.0,
      "text": "where you can see the 40-year-old intern in the midst of all the college interns."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 479360.0,
      "end_time": 482536.0,
      "text": "And then, courtesy of Fox Business News,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 482560.0,
      "end_time": 485736.0,
      "text": "they called the concept \"The 50-Year-Old Intern.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 485760.0,
      "end_time": 489575.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 489600.0,
      "end_time": 493456.0,
      "text": "So five of the biggest financial services companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 493480.0,
      "end_time": 497616.0,
      "text": "have reentry internship programs for returning finance professionals."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 497640.0,
      "end_time": 500936.0,
      "text": "And at this point, hundreds of people have participated."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 500960.0,
      "end_time": 502736.0,
      "text": "These internships are paid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 502760.0,
      "end_time": 505496.0,
      "text": "and the people who move on to permanent roles"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 505520.0,
      "end_time": 508200.0,
      "text": "are commanding competitive salaries."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 508680.0,
      "end_time": 512135.0,
      "text": "And now, seven of the biggest engineering companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 512159.0,
      "end_time": 516456.0,
      "text": "are piloting reentry internship programs for returning engineers"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 516480.0,
      "end_time": 520200.0,
      "text": "as part of an initiative with the Society of Women Engineers."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 521558.99999999994,
      "end_time": 525400.0,
      "text": "Now, why are companies embracing the reentry internship?"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 526440.0,
      "end_time": 529416.0,
      "text": "Because the internship allows the employer"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 529440.0,
      "end_time": 533456.0,
      "text": "to base their hiring decision on an actual work sample"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 533480.0,
      "end_time": 535535.0,
      "text": "instead of a series of interviews,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 535559.0,
      "end_time": 539295.0,
      "text": "and the employer does not have to make that permanent hiring decision"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 539320.0,
      "end_time": 542120.0,
      "text": "until the internship period is over."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 542640.0,
      "end_time": 546536.0,
      "text": "This testing out period removes the perceived risk"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 546560.0,
      "end_time": 550136.0,
      "text": "that some managers attach to hiring relaunchers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 550160.0,
      "end_time": 552815.0,
      "text": "and they are attracting excellent candidates"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 552840.0,
      "end_time": 554680.0,
      "text": "who are turning into great hires."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 555240.0,
      "end_time": 557200.0,
      "text": "Think about how far we have come."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 557560.0,
      "end_time": 560536.0,
      "text": "Before this, most employers were not interested"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 560560.0,
      "end_time": 562896.0,
      "text": "in engaging with relaunchers at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 562920.0,
      "end_time": 566415.0,
      "text": "But now, not only are programs being developed"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 566440.0,
      "end_time": 568976.0,
      "text": "specifically with relaunchers in mind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 569000.0,
      "end_time": 571496.0,
      "text": "but you can&#39;t even apply for these programs"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 571520.0,
      "end_time": 574199.0,
      "text": "unless you have a gap on your résumé."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 574840.0,
      "end_time": 576936.0,
      "text": "This is the mark of real change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 576960.0,
      "end_time": 579216.0,
      "text": "of true institutional shift,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 579240.0,
      "end_time": 582776.0,
      "text": "because if we can solve this problem for relaunchers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 582800.0,
      "end_time": 586960.0,
      "text": "we can solve it for other career transitioners too."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 586120.0,
      "end_time": 588560.0,
      "text": "In fact, an employer just told me"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 588800.0,
      "end_time": 590576.0,
      "text": "that their veterans return to work program"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 590600.0,
      "end_time": 593976.0,
      "text": "is based on their reentry internship program."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 594000.0,
      "end_time": 599160.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;s no reason why there can&#39;t be a retiree internship program."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 599400.0,
      "end_time": 601520.0,
      "text": "Different pool, same concept."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 602400.0,
      "end_time": 604856.0,
      "text": "So let me tell you what happened with Tracy Shapiro."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 604880.0,
      "end_time": 607456.0,
      "text": "Remember that she had to tell everyone she knew"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 607480.0,
      "end_time": 609480.0,
      "text": "about her interest in returning to work."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 609800.0,
      "end_time": 613976.0,
      "text": "Well, one critical conversation with another parent in her community"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 614000.0,
      "end_time": 616960.0,
      "text": "led to a job offer for Tracy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 616120.0,
      "end_time": 618896.0,
      "text": "and it was an accounting job in a finance department."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 618920.0,
      "end_time": 620240.0,
      "text": "But it was a temp job."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 620800.0,
      "end_time": 623256.0,
      "text": "The company told her there was a possibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 623280.0,
      "end_time": 626815.0,
      "text": "it could turn into something more, but no guarantees."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 626840.0,
      "end_time": 629200.0,
      "text": "This was in the fall of 2011."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 629720.0,
      "end_time": 632736.0,
      "text": "Tracy loved this company, and she loved the people"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 632760.0,
      "end_time": 635816.0,
      "text": "and the office was less than 10 minutes from her house."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 635840.0,
      "end_time": 638560.0,
      "text": "So even though she had a second job offer"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 638800.0,
      "end_time": 640976.0,
      "text": "at another company for a permanent full-time role,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 641000.0,
      "end_time": 644216.0,
      "text": "she decided to take her chances with this internship"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 644240.0,
      "end_time": 646000.0,
      "text": "and hope for the best."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 647320.0,
      "end_time": 650376.0,
      "text": "Well, she ended up blowing away all of their expectations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 650400.0,
      "end_time": 652896.0,
      "text": "and the company not only made her a permanent offer"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 652920.0,
      "end_time": 655160.0,
      "text": "at the beginning of 2012,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 655400.0,
      "end_time": 657656.0,
      "text": "but they made it even more interesting and challenging,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 657680.0,
      "end_time": 659800.0,
      "text": "because they knew what Tracy could handle."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 660400.0,
      "end_time": 662856.0,
      "text": "Fast forward to 2015,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 662880.0,
      "end_time": 664456.0,
      "text": "Tracy&#39;s been promoted."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 664480.0,
      "end_time": 666896.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ve paid for her to get her MBA at night."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 666920.0,
      "end_time": 670240.0,
      "text": "She&#39;s even hired another relauncher to work for her."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 671840.0,
      "end_time": 675216.0,
      "text": "Tracy&#39;s temp job was a tryout,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 675240.0,
      "end_time": 676896.0,
      "text": "just like an internship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 676920.0,
      "end_time": 682160.0,
      "text": "and it ended up being a win for both Tracy and her employer."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 683600.0,
      "end_time": 687976.0,
      "text": "Now, my goal is to bring the reentry internship concept"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 688000.0,
      "end_time": 690736.0,
      "text": "to more and more employers."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 690760.0,
      "end_time": 692576.0,
      "text": "But in the meantime,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 692600.0,
      "end_time": 695816.0,
      "text": "if you are returning to work after a career break,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 695840.0,
      "end_time": 701856.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t hesitate to suggest an internship or an internship-like arrangement"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 701880.0,
      "end_time": 707496.0,
      "text": "to an employer that does not have a formal reentry internship program."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 707520.0,
      "end_time": 709816.0,
      "text": "Be their first success story,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 709840.0,
      "end_time": 713480.0,
      "text": "and you can be the example for more relaunchers to come."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 713920.0,
      "end_time": 715136.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 715160.0,
      "end_time": 720324.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}